Definition: in a keen or penetrating way
Example: he was keenly aware of his own shortcomings; she pitied her sister acutely; acutely aware
Synonyms: adj, all, perceptive, keen, acutely, acute, in, a, or, penetrating, way, he, was, aware, of, his, own, shortcomings, she, pitied, her, sister
Category: adv.all
